  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1214">
<l>kaṉaviṉā luṇṭākuṅ kāma naṉaviṉāl </l>
<l> nalkārai nāṭit taraṟku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is pleasure in my dream, because in it I seek and obtain him who does not visit me in my wakefulness.</l>
            </lg>
